Faa'iidada kororka ee kororka ee cudurka Coronavirus (COVID-19) ee Midowga Yurub / Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Ingiriiska, laga bilaabo 1da Janaayo ilaa 15ka Maarso 2020
Tirada guud ee kiisaska cudurka Coronavirus (COVID-19) waxay muujineysaa isbeddel la mid ah waddamada Midowga Yurub/Gobolka Dhaqaalaha Yurub iyo Boqortooyada Ingiriiska taas oo xaqiijineysa in cudurka faafa ee COVID-19 uu si dhakhso leh u sii kordhayaa dhammaan wadamada iyadoo la adeegsanayo marxalado kala duwan oo ku saleysan waddanka.
Iyada oo ku saleysan khibrada Talyaaniga, wadamada, isbitaalada iyo cutubyada daryeelka degdega ah waa inay sii kordhiyaan diyaar garowgooda kor u kaca xawaaraha degdega ah ee bukaanka COVID-19 ee u baahan daryeel caafimaad, gaar ahaan daryeel degdeg ah.
31 December 2019 Koox ka mid ah kiisaska cudurka 'pneumonia' oo aan la aqoon cudurka ayaa lagu soo wargeliyay Wuhan, Gobolka Hubei, Shiinaha.
9ka Janaayo 2020 Xarunta Xakamaynta iyo Ka-hortagga Cudurada, Shiinaha ayaa u sheegtay inay tahay cudur-darrada Novel Coronavirus, oo hadda loo yaqaan 'Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2' (SARS-CoV-2).
Tan iyo markaas, cudurka ka dhashay cudurka SARS-CoV-2 ayaa loo magacaabay cudurka Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Caddaynta ilaa hadda waxay muujineysaa in 80% dadka qaba COVID-19 ay leeyihiin cudur fudud, taas oo ah cudurrada neefsashada ee leh ama aan lahayn cudurka sanbabada, inta badanna ay ka bogsadaan.
14% kiisaska, COVID-19 waxay u muuqataa inay tahay cudur aad u daran oo u baahan cusbitaal, halka 6% kiisaska kale ay leeyihiin aragti xanuun daran oo u baahan daryeel culus.
Dhimashada bukaanka la dhigay isbitaalka COVID-19 waxay qiyaastii tahay 4%.
Daraasaddan, waxaan qiimeynay isbeddelka guud ee COVID-19 ee waddan kasta oo ka tirsan Midowga Yurub / Aagga Dhaqaalaha Yurub (EU/EEA) iyo Boqortooyada Ingiriiska (UK) oo aan isbarbardhignay gobolka Xubey ee Shiinaha.
Waxaan sidoo kale isbarbardhignaa tirada hadda jirta ee kiisaska COVID-19 ee dalalka EU/EEA iyo UK intii u dhaxaysay 31 Janaayo - 15 Maarso 2020 iyadoo la barbar dhigo Talyaaniga.
Kiisaska COVID-19 ee dalalka EU/EEA iyo UK
Shiinaha kadib, COVID-19 ayaa sii ballaariyay dhulka, waxaana hadda ka horraysa wadamada kale ee adduunka waxqabadka cudurka faafa ee COVID-19.
Bishii Maarso 11, 2020, Agaasimaha Guud ee Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa COVID-19 ku dhawaaqay cudur faafa.
Daabacaadda 5-ka Maarso ee Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. ayaa soo bandhigtay kiisaska ugu horreeya ee COVID-19 ee Yurub la xaqiijiyay sida ku cad qeexitaanka kiiska WHO.
EU/EEA, Faransiisku wuxuu soo sheegay saddexda kiis ee ugu horreeya ee la xaqiijiyay ee dadka ka soo laabtay Wuhan, Gobolka Hubei, Shiinaha, 24ka Janaayo 2020.
Ilaa 15 Maarso 2020, dhammaan 30 waddanka EU/EEA iyo Boqortooyada Ingiriiska (UK) ayaa laga helay kiisaska COVID-19, iyadoo 17,750 kiis iyo 1,441 dhimashada laga soo sheegay Talyaaniga oo keliya, iyadoo 39,768 kiis iyo 1,727 dhimashada laga soo sheegay 31ka Diseembar 2019 iyo taariikhdaas.
Hel tirada guud ee kiisaska COVID-19 iyo ballaarinta guud
Xarunta Yurub ee Ka-hortagga iyo Xakamaynta Cudurrada (ECDC) waxaa lagu cusbooneysiiyay maalin kasta 8:00 subaxnimo tirakoobka kiisaska COVID-19 ee laga helay waddan kasta oo adduunka ah oo laga helay ilo rasmi ah sida Wasaaradaha Caafimaadka ee waddamada, Hay'adaha Caafimaadka Qaranka iyo Goboleedyada iyo WHO.
Xogtan ayaa loo adeegsaday in lagu qiimeeyo isbeddellada COVID-19 ee EU/EEA iyo UK loona barbardhigo cudurka ka dhacay Talyaaniga.
Annaga oo ah wakiilka faafitaanka kiisaska COVID-19 ee firfircoon, waxaan si fudud u xisaabinay 14 maalmood oo gaaban oo guud oo kiisaska COVID-19 ah iyadoo la tixgelinayo habdhaqanka dabiiciga ah ee COVID-19 ee waddan kasta oo EU/EEA ah iyo UK intii u dhaxaysay 1da Janaayo - 15 Maarso 2020.
Waxaan sidoo kale soo bandhignay tirada guud ee kiisaska la soo sheegay ee dal kasta ilaa 8:00 AM ee 15 March 2020 marka loo eego Talyaaniga intii u dhaxaysay 31 Janaayo - 15 Maarso 2020.
COVID-19 ee ka socda waddamada EU/EEA iyo UK
14 maalmood oo gaaban oo ku saabsan kiisaska COVID-19 ee ku baahsan waddamada EU/EEA iyo UK ayaa caadi ahaan la raaco gobolka Hubei (Shiinaha) (shaxda 1).
EU/EEA iyo guud ahaan UK, guud ahaan faafitaanka COVID-19 wuxuu bilaabay inuu kordho 21 Febraayo wuxuuna si dhakhso leh u kordhay 28 Febraayo 2020 (waxyaabaha dheeriga ah).
Tani waxay ugu horreyntii sabab u ahayd kororka xawaaraha xawaaraha ee laga soo sheegay Talyaaniga, laakiin dhammaan waddamada kale ee EU/EEA iyo UK waxay ku aragtay isbedel la mid ah kororka COVID-19 ee guud ahaan (waxyaabo dheeri ah).
Sawirka 2 wuxuu muujinayaa tirada guud ee kiisaska COVID-19 ee 31ka Janaayo - 15ka Maarso 2020 marka loo eego wadamada EU/EEA iyo UK marka loo eego Talyaaniga.
Tani waxay si gaar ah u muujineysaa in ilaa 8:00 subaxnimo ee Maarso 15, 15 waddan oo kale oo EU/EEA ah iyo UK ay horeyba u soo sheegeen tirada guud ee kiisaska la midka ah kiisaska Talyaaniga 3 toddobaad ka hor ama ka yar.
Natiijooyinkayagu waxay tilmaamayaan in tirada kiisaska COVID-19 ee la soo sheegay ay si degdeg ah u kordhayaan EU/EEA iyo UK.
Isbeddelka la arkay ee baahinta COVID-19 wuxuu muujinayaa in masiibada ay ku sii kordheyso xawaare isbarbardhig ah dhammaan wadamada.
Tani waxay ku jirto inkastoo ay jiraan heerar kala duwan oo wadamada, kala duwanaanshaha jawaabaha caafimaadka dadweynaha ee qaranka iyo qeexitaanno kiis oo laga yaabo inay kala duwan yihiin wadamada iyo borotokool kala duwan oo lagu dooranayo bukaannada, kuwaas oo loo baahan yahay in la hubiyo xaqiijinta COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan qabashada iyo baaritaanka.
Bilowgii Maarso 2020, dhakhaatiir ku sugan aagagga saameynta leh ee Talyaaniga ayaa sheegay xaalad ay ku baahanyihiin 10% bukaanka qaba COVID-19 daryeel degdeg ah, ilaha warbaahinta ayaa sheegay in isbitaalada iyo cutubyada daryeelka degdegga ah ee aagaggaas ay horeyba u gaareen awoodooda ugu badan.
Tirakoobka cusbitaalka iyo/ama rugta daryeelka degdegga ah ee kiisaska COVID-19 ayaa hadda la heli karaa heerka EU/EEA oo kaliya 6% iyo 1% kiisaska siday u kala horreeyaan (tirakoobka lama muujiyo).
Si kastaba ha noqotee, waa in loo ururiyaa si taxane ah si loo buuxiyo xogta kormeerka ee hadda jirta oo diiradda saaraya tirada kiisaska la soo sheegay iyo tirada dhimashada.
Daraasad lagu sameeyay 2010-11 waxay aragtay farqi weyn oo ku saabsan helitaanka sariiraha daryeelka degdegga ah iyo kuwa dhexdhexaadka ah ee Yurub, laga bilaabo 29.2 Jarmalka ilaa 4.2 sariirood oo loogu talagalay 100,000 oo qof.
Taas macnaheedu waa in wadamada ay heli karaan ilo ka badan ama ka yar Talyaaniga (12.5 sariiro daryeel deggan iyo sariiro daryeel dhexdhexaad ah oo 100,000 oo qof sanadkii 2010-11).
Faafida kiisaska COVID-19 ee isbitaalka ee la xiriira 90% halista awoodda sariirta daryeelka degdegga ah, iyadoo la qiyaaso in la qiyaaso waddan kasta oo EU/EEA ah iyo UK, ayaa lagu soo bandhigay casriyeynta xaaladaha la xiriira buuxinta awoodda daryeelka caafimaadka ee lagu qiimeeyo COVID-19 ee ECDC ee sixth update.
Maaddaama kiisaska ay weli ku jiraan kooxo ku yaal waddamada EU/EEA iyo qaar ka mid ah gobollada UK, isbitaalada iyo cutubyada daryeelka degdegga ahna ay u adeegaan dadweynaha gobolka sida caadiga ah loo qeexay, macluumaadka ku saabsan kiisaska iyo sariiraha daryeelka degdegga ah waa in lagu siiyaa heerka ugu horreeya ee Nomenclature of Territorial Units for Statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Khibrada ka timid Talyaaniga iyo isbeddellada hadda jira ee dalalka kale waxay muujinayaan in cudurka faafa ee COVID-19 uu si dhakhso leh ugu sii kordhayaa EU/EEA iyo UK.
Wadamada, isbitaalada iyo xarumaha daryeelka degdegga ah waa inay isu diyaariyaan xaaladaha gudbinta bulshada ee SARS-CoV-2 iyo kororka tirada bukaannada COVID-19 ee u baahan daryeel caafimaad, gaar ahaan daryeelka degdegga ah sida ku dhaca aagagga saameynta leh ee Talyaaniga.
Sida lagu muujiyey qiimeynta khatarta degdegga ah ee dhawaan ee ECDC, iyadoo isbeddelka aragtida xaddidan ee xaddidan laga joojinayo, habka degdegga ah, horey loo qabtay iyo qaab ballaaran ayaa loo baahan yahay si loo yareeyo faafitaanka SARS-CoV-2, maadaama haddii aan la hirgelin waqtiga, kororka degdegga ah ee la filayo ee tirada kiisaska laga yaabo inaysan siin waqti ku filan go'aan qaadayaasha iyo isbitaalada si ay u fahmaan, u aqbalaan oo ay u hagaajiyaan jawaabtooda.
Qiimaynta halista degdegga ah waxay sidoo kale liis gareysaa tallaabooyinka caafimaadka dadweynaha ee looga hortago saameynta masiibada.
Wadamada waxay fursado yar u leeyihiin inay sii kordhiyaan dadaalkooda xakamaynta iyo yareynta cadaadiska daryeelka caafimaadka si loo yareeyo faafitaanka SARS-CoV-2.
Haddii ay taasi fashilmaan, waxaa jira fursad weyn oo nidaamyada daryeelka caafimaadka ee dalalka kale ee EU / EEA ay la kulmi doonaan koror degdeg ah oo bukaanada u baahan daryeel degdeg ah maalmaha ama usbuucyada soo socda.
Koronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) oo sababay cudurka SARS-CoV-2 ayaa ilaa hadda dilay in ka badan 3,000 oo qof, waxaana cudurka ku dhacay in ka badan 80,000 oo qof oo Shiinaha iyo meelo kale oo adduunka ah, taas oo keentay musiibo aadanaha.
Sida fayraska SARS-CoV ee u eg, kaas oo sababiyay kumanaan qof inay qabaan SARS sanadkii 2003, SARS-CoV-2 waxay u badan tahay inay ku faafiyeen duqsiyo waxayna soo saaraan astaamo la mid ah habka waxqabadka.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, COVID-19 wuxuu leeyahay heerar hooseeya oo halis ah iyo heerka dhimashada marka loo eego SARS, laakiin waa mid aad u faafa oo saameyn badan ku leh ragga iyo dumarka waayeelka ah marka loo eego dhalinyarada.
Iyada oo la jawaabayo tirada daabacaadda ee kor u kaca ee cudurrada soo ifbaxa, maqaalkani wuxuu isku dayaa inuu bixiyo dib u eegis joogto ah oo ballaaran oo ku saabsan mawduuca cilmi baarista ee si dhakhso leh u soo koraya.
Waxaan ka koobnaan doonnaa aasaaska cudurrada - sayniska, cilmiga cudurrada, cilmiga fayrasyada, cudurrada, daaweynta, saadaasha iyo ka hortagga.
Inkastoo su'aalo badan ay weli jiraan jawaabaha ay tahay in la helo, waxaan rajeyneynaa in dib u eegiskani uu gacan ka geysan doono fahamka cudurka dilaaga ah iyo baabi'inta.
Sababtoo ah faafitaanka cudurka cusub ee loo yaqaan 'Novel viral disease' ayaa ah in gu'ga ee 25ka Janaayo, 2020, uu noqdo xusuus aan la filayn oo aan la iloobin dhammaan dadka Shiinaha, kuwaas oo la weydiiyay inay guriga joogaan fasax oo dhan iyo dhowr toddobaad ka dib.
Fayraska ayaa aad ugu eg Coronavirus (CoV) oo keentay cudurka SARS ee 2003-kii; sidaa darteed, Febraayo 11, 2020 waxaa loogu magac daray SARS-CoV-2 ee Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) waxaana la magacaabay cudurka la xiriira COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Cudurka ayaa ka bilaabmay Wuhan, Shiinaha wuxuuna si dhakhso leh ugu faafay dalka oo dhan iyo ku dhawaad 50 dal oo kale oo adduunka ah.
Ilaa 2da Maarso 2020, waxaa jira in ka badan 80,000 kiis oo la xaqiijiyay oo COVID-19 ah, iyadoo in ka badan 40,000 oo bukaan ah ay isbitaal ka baxeen cudurka, iyo in ka badan 3,000 oo bukaan ah ay dhinteen.
WHO waxay ka digtay in COVID-19 uu yahay cadowga ugu weyn ee dadweynaha iyo in uu ka xoog badan yahay argagixisada.
Sida laga soo xigtay PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), in ka yar laba bilood ka dib markii la soo saaray warbixintii ugu horreysay ee 7 January 2020, in ka badan 200 oo maqaallood ayaa lagu daabacay COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan fayrasyada, cudurrada faafa, sayniska, cilmi baarista, baaritaanka, iyo daaweynta, taas oo keentay in fayraska loo kala saaro bukaanno badan.
Dib u eegiskani wuxuu isku dayaa inuu soo bandhigo horumarka cilmi baarista ee ku saabsan mawduucyada cusub iyo kuwa si dhakhso leh u soo koraya.
Mar kasta oo ay suurtagal tahay, waxaan isku dayi doonaa inaan isbarbardhigno COVID-19 cudurrada kale ee ay keenaan SARS iyo CoV, oo ah cudurada neefsashada ee Bariga Dhexe (MERS, 2012).
Waxaan ka wada hadli doonnaa wixii aan hadda ka baranay ka hortagga iyo saadaasha cudurka iyo sidoo kale qaar ka mid ah su 'aalaha kale ee muhiimka ah.
CoVs waxaa loo arkaa inay yihiin cudur aan waxyeello u geysan karin dadka, iyadoo ay u horseedaan qiyaastii 15% qabowga caadiga ah ee jiilaalka 4.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, qarnigii la soo dhaafay waxaan laba jeer la kulannay cudurrada aadka u daran ee loo yaqaan 'COVs' ee aadka u nugul, kuwaas oo ah SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV, kuwaas oo asal ahaan u horseeday faafitaankii Shiinaha 2003 iyo Sacuudi Carabiya 2012 siday u kala horreeyaan waxayna si dhakhso leh ugu faafay dalal kale oo leh heerar caafimaad oo aad u daran iyo heerar dhimashada.
Sidaa darteed, COVID-19-ka hadda jira waa cudurka COVID-19 ee saddexaad ee taariikhda bini aadamka ee la diiwaangeliyey.
Sida lagu muujiyey sawirka 1.1, kooxaha cudurka sanbabada, asalkoodu aan la garanayn, ayaa markii ugu horreysay laga soo wargeliyay Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha ee Wuhan, 31 December 2019.
Toddoba maalmood ka dib ayaa la sii daayay taxanaha COVID.
Kiiskii ugu horreeyay ee dhimashada ayaa laga soo sheegay Wuhan 15ka Janaayo 2020.
Inta lagu jiro, cudurku wuxuu si dhakhso leh ugu faafay magaalooyinka, gobollada iyo waddamada ku xeeran.
Janaayo 20, waxaa la sheegay in la helay cudurrada bixiyeyaasha daryeelka caafimaadka, taas oo muujineysa in cudurka laga faafi karo bini-aadamka.
Janaayo 23, magaalada Wuhan ayaa la xiray iyadoo dhammaan gaadiidka dadweynaha la xiray.
Daraasad caafimaad oo hore oo ku saabsan cudurka oo la sameeyay 24ka Janaayo ayaa lagu sheegay in 21 ka mid ah 41 bukaan oo kiis la xaqiijiyay ay xiriir toos ah la lahaayeen suuqa badda ee Wuhan, oo loo maleynayo inay tahay meesha ugu horreysa ee cudurka laga soo qaato ilo xayawaan oo aan la garanayn.
Janaayo 30, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday cudurka masiibada caafimaadka adduunka.
