Enzyme-defaulting angiotensin 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xiran dusha sare ee unugyada (qandhadaha unugyada) ee sanbabada, dareemayaasha, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo mindhicirka.
ACE2 waxay isku dheelitirtaa firfircoonida enzymes-ka la xiriira angiotensin-beddelayaha (ACE) iyadoo la yareynayo qadarka angiotensin-II iyo kordhinta angiotensin (1-7) taas oo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameedyo daawo ah oo rajo leh daaweynta cudurrada wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa sidii barta gelitaanka unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
Nooca bini'aadamka ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Enzyme-defaulting angiotensin 2 waa metaloenzyme zinc-ku jira oo ku yaal heerarka gudaha iyo dusha unugyada kale.
Protein-ka ACE2 wuxuu leeyahay domain-ka N-terminal peptidease M2 iyo domain-ka C-terminal electrin-ka amino acid-ka.
ACE2 waa nooc I oo ah borotiinka qanjirka ah ee mara mara oo leh heerka enzymatically-ka ah ee aan la soo saarin dusha sare ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded ee unfolded.
Xagga ka baxsan unugyada ACE2 waxaa ka soo jeeda xageeda shadehyada kale ee loo yaqaan 'shadez', waxaana ka soo baxa protein-ka dhalaalaya ee loo sameeyay dhiigga oo la sii daayo, ugu dambeynna waxaa lagu soo saaraa cirbadda.
ACE2 waxay ku jirtaa xubnaha badankood: ACE2 waxay ugu weyn ku xiran tahay unugyada sanbabada ee nooca II, unugyada qanjirka hoose ee qanjirka hoose, unugyada qanjirka hoose ee dareenka iyo neerfaha, iyo unugyada unugyada dareenka jilicsan ee xubnaha badankood.
