Daraasadaha loo sameeyay chlorokwin iyo hydroxychloroquine oo la socda ama aan lahayn azithromycin ayaa leh xaddidaadyo waaweyn, taas oo ka hortagey bulshada caafimaadka inay qaataan daaweyntaas iyada oo aan la helin daraasad dheeri ah. Osaltamivir ma xakameeyo SARS-CoV-2 oo ah daaweynta COVID-19.
Kordhinta xaddiga cytokine ee marxaladaha COVID-19 ee ka dambeeya waxay noqon kartaa dhibaato.
Waxaa jira caddayn muujinaya in hydroxychloroquine ay leedahay sifooyinka ka hortagga kororka tirooyinka cytokine. Koorsada yar ee la dhammeystiray ayaa lagu daray Toqulizumab tilmaamaha daaweynta ee Shirkadda Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha.
Waxay ku jirtaa tallaabo heer qaran oo heerka 2 ah oo aan kala sooc lahayn Talyaaniga kadib markii ay muujisay natiijooyin wanaagsan dadka qaba cudur culus.
Waxaa lagu daray baaritaan dhiig oo loo sameeyay serum feritine si loo ogaado kororka tirada cytokine, waxaana loogu talagalay in la hortago kororka noocan oo kale ah, taas oo loo maleynayo inay sabab u tahay dhimashada dadka qaar ee saameeyay.
Interleukin-6 anti-depressant waxaa FDA-da ansixisay 2017 si loogu daaweeyo cudurka 'steroid-reactive cytokine release syndrome' oo sabab ka duwan, CAR T cell therapy.
Ilaa hadda ma jirto wax caddayn ah oo aan kala sooc lahayn oo la xakameyn karo oo muujinaya in Tocilizumab uu yahay daaweyn wax ku ool ah oo loogu talagalay CRS.
